{"tid":1289441,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"「老貓燒鬚」今之真係比人Hack撚左 2","createTime":"2019-07-06T05:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:07:46.000Z","uid":9769,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"00d5ebf987b108a259a3095b2fa914c1580cd3ae","tid":1289441,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">事發經過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">樓主1:</span><br />\n================================<br />\n前幾個禮拜都覺得奇怪啦，無啦啦多咗個IP register咗係隻linksys<br />\n問題係搵晒成間屋都唔係好覺見過呢個mac address<br />\n今日見條撚樣online，port scan佢係零反應，似係drop packet<br />\n之後router開log睇下條撚樣駁去邊，仲唔比我搵到你駁咗去邊<br />\n屌你老母駁撚咗去aws，但係唔撚知個IP係邊啲公司嘅<br />\n請問有無方法知道呢啲IP真正主人係邊個?<br />\n54.182.0.95<br />\n<a href=\"http://server-54-182-0-95.hkg51.r.cloudfront.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserver-54-182-0-95.hkg51.r.cloudfront.net&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=7289fbc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://server-54-182-0-95.hkg51.r.cloudfront.net</a><br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">樓主2:</span><br />\n================================<br />\n都應該夠料做野<br />\n止咗血先，中英數10個位wifi password都hack撚到入嚟，真係痴撚線<br />\n似乎我棟大廈有某個高手有一堆display card去hack個wifi<br />\n<br />\n條撚樣mac address<br />\n5C:52:1E:92:31:BE<br />\n大家見到係router ban 9佢<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打 「<span style=\"color: gold;\">細佬Rafael</span>」回覆：<br />\n================================<br />\nMAC Address/OUI Vendor {Company}<br />\n5C:52:1E Nintendo Co.,Ltd<br />\n<br />\nSwitch???<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">樓主3:</span><br />\n================================<br />\nOh fuck, 真係我部switch<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">眾巴打：</span><br />\n================================<br />\n恥笑開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n================================"},{"pid":"320a129185fb8cd6d7a647026f12fc6889bca202","tid":1289441,"uid":203413,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"一燒鬚成千古恨"},{"pid":"814050a257263132896628867aeb705ea97de8f9","tid":1289441,"uid":9769,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"320a129185fb8cd6d7a647026f12fc6889bca202","tid":1289441,"uid":203413,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"一燒鬚成千古恨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c07906d95288e9ca62efaab0f8c455366c1cd2a","tid":1289441,"uid":232077,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戇鳩戀童變態樓主<br />\n你收檔啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咪忘記仲有個戀童犯Agentcc (田少雄）係度<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cEskQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cEskQT</a>"},{"pid":"8b024aeb65844ae9f0c31fe16e65855a64069a9a","tid":1289441,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戀童監躉</span><br />\n<blockquote>會員Agentcc原來係孌童犯，搞細路女坐監(1):<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/386856/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/386856/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n話說有位會員Agentcc因為分享佢坐監生活而出名<br />\n<br />\n佢仲成日出post炫耀北上叫雞<br />\n<br />\n深圳香格里拉田雞煲+蒸原隻大元貝